{"word":"χαράκωμα","slug":"χαράκωμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χαράκωμα</b></el> <el>(χᾰράκωμα, ατος, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χαρακόω'><el>χαρακόω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a place paled round, an entrenched camp</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a palisade, rampart</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>vallum</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}